---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="How Professional Web Design Shelby NC Drives More Local Leads in 2026"
  description="Learn how professional web design and local SEO work together to drive more leads for Shelby, NC businesses in 2026."
>
  <article class="pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0A0A0A]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Header -->
      <header class="mb-16 text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-6 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-cyan/20 bg-brand-cyan/5">
          <span class="text-brand-cyan text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Vol #2 Article #11</span>
          <span class="w-1 h-1 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/30"></span>
          <span class="text-brand-sky/60 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-widest">June 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-heading text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-8 tracking-tight leading-[1.1]">
          How Professional Web Design Shelby NC <br />
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-cyan to-brand-blue">Drives More Local Leads in 2026</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-sky/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Local customers are actively searching for "web designers near me" — not because they want to build websites, but because they need trustworthy local service providers. Your website is often their first impression.
        </p>
      </header>

      <!-- Main Image Placeholder -->
      <div class="aspect-video bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 rounded-3xl mb-16 overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative group">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue/20 to-transparent opacity-50 group-hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
           <span class="text-brand-sky/20 font-heading text-4xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] transform -rotate-12">Shelby Web Company Official</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-brand-sky/90 mb-12">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-cyan hover:underline decoration-brand-cyan/30 underline-offset-4">Shelby Web Company</a> creates web design Shelby that turns visitors into customers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">01.</span> What Makes a High-Converting Website
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Clear, benefit-focused messaging</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Tell your customers exactly how you solve their problems from the moment they land on your site.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Strong calls-to-action on every page</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Make it incredibly easy for customers to call, text, or book your services.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Professional visuals and branding</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Build instant trust with a modern, clean design that reflects your quality of work.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 hover:border-brand-blue/20 transition-all">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Fast, reliable performance</h3>
            <p class="text-brand-sky/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">Ensure your site loads instantly on all devices so you don't lose impatient leads.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-blue/5 border-l-4 border-brand-blue p-8 my-12 rounded-r-2xl">
          <p class="text-white font-medium italic mb-0">"Local SEO optimization from day one: Appear in front of customers exactly when they are searching for your local services."</p>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/60 text-sm mt-4 mb-0">— Shelby Web Company Strategy</p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">02.</span> The Power of Combining Web Design + Local SEO
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">
          Many companies offer either design or SEO. As a full-service SEO agency Shelby, we do both. This integrated approach means your new website starts ranking faster and generating leads sooner.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-brand-dark border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-3xl mb-16">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Dominating the "Map Pack"</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-sky/70 mb-0">
            Did you know that 46% of all Google searches have local intent? When we build your site, we structure your schema markup and local landing pages so Google recognizes you as the authority in Shelby. This is how you land in the "Top 3" map results, which command 70% of the clicks.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8 flex items-center gap-4">
          <span class="text-brand-accent">03.</span> Anatomy of a High-Converting Page
        </h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-8">To turn a Shelby visitor into a lead, every page needs these three elements:</p>
        
        <ul class="space-y-6 list-none p-0 mb-16">
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">1</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block mb-1">The Hero Hook</strong>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/70">A clear value proposition that answers "What do you do?" in 3 seconds.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">2</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Social Proof</strong>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/70">Actual reviews from Shelby locals to build instant credibility.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-cyan/10 border border-brand-cyan/20 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-cyan font-bold text-sm">3</div>
            <div>
              <strong class="text-white block mb-1">Frictionless CTA</strong>
              <span class="text-brand-sky/70">A prominent, easy-to-use button to book or call immediately.</span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-8">Proven Results for Local Businesses</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-sky/80 mb-12">Our clients consistently report big increases in:</p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-24">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl text-brand-cyan mb-4">↑</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold">Organic Traffic</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl text-brand-cyan mb-4">✆</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold">Phone Calls & Forms</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark/30 border border-white/5 p-8 rounded-2xl text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl text-brand-cyan mb-4">$</div>
            <div class="text-white font-bold">Overall Revenue</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Section -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-brand-dark p-12 rounded-[2rem] text-center relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_50%_50%,rgba(132,204,22,0.1),transparent_70%)]"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 relative z-10">Ready to Grow Your Shelby Business Online?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-10 relative z-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Whether you need a full redesign or a brand-new site, our web designers near me are here to help you succeed.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center relative z-10">
            <a href="/contact" class="bg-brand-accent text-[#0A0A0A] px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-brand-accent-light transition-all">
              Claim Your Offer
            </a>
            <a href="tel:7044738188" class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md text-white border border-white/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-white/20 transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"/></svg>
              (704) 473-8188
            </a>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm mt-8 relative z-10">
            Limited-Time Offer: Free logo design + $100 referral bonus with any website package.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer navigation -->
      <footer class="mt-24 pt-12 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-wrap gap-8 items-center justify-between">
        <a href="/blog" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
          Back to Blog
        </a>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a>
          <a href="/services/web-design" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Web Design</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="text-brand-sky/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
